#: ../../source/user_guide/dataframe/io.rst:2
msgid "Data input and output"
msgstr "数据输入和输出"

#: ../../source/user_guide/dataframe/io.rst:6
msgid "MaxCompute"
msgstr "大数据计算服务"

#: ../../source/user_guide/dataframe/io.rst:9
msgid "Read and convert to tables"
msgstr "读取并转换为表格"

#: ../../source/user_guide/dataframe/io.rst:10
msgid ""
"Users can create MaxFrame DataFrame objects from MaxCompute tables with "
":func:`read_odps_table` , and store computed results into MaxCompute "
"tables with :func:`DataFrame.to_odps_table`."
msgstr ""
"用户可以使用 :func:`read_odps_table` 创建来自大数据计算服务表的 MaxFrame "
"DataFrame 对象，并使用 :func:`DataFrame.to_odps_table` 将计算结果存储到大"
"数据计算服务表中。"

#: ../../source/user_guide/dataframe/io.rst:13
msgid ""
"For instance, if you want to get data from non-partitioned table "
"`test_odps_table`, do some transformation by MaxFrame and store it into "
"another partitioned table `test_processed_odps_table`, you may use "
":func:`read_odps_table` as is shown below."
msgstr ""
"例如，如果您想从非分区表 `test_odps_table` 获取数据，通过 MaxFrame 进行"
"一些转换，并将其存储到另一个分区表 `test_processed_odps_table` 中，您可以"
"使用 :func:`read_odps_table` 如下所示。"

#: ../../source/user_guide/dataframe/io.rst:25
msgid ""
"If the table is partitioned, ``read_odps_table`` will read data from all "
"partitions which should be definitely avoided if there are a number of "
"partitions. You can select one partition or a number of partitions with "
"``partitions`` argument."
msgstr ""
"如果表是分区的，``read_odps_table`` 将从所有分区读取数据，如果存在多个"
"分区，这应被绝对避免。您可以通过 ``partitions`` 参数选择一个分区或多个"
"分区。"

#: ../../source/user_guide/dataframe/io.rst:35
msgid ""
"Values of partition columns are not included in results by default. If "
"you need these values, you may specify ``append_partitions=True``."
msgstr ""
"默认情况下，分区列的值不会包含在结果中。如果您需要这些值，您可以指定 ``"
"append_partitions=True``。"

#: ../../source/user_guide/dataframe/io.rst:44
msgid ""
"The resulting DataFrame will produce a RangeIndex by default. You may use"
" ``index_col`` argument to specify existing columns as indexes."
msgstr ""
"默认情况下，生成的 DataFrame 将产生 RangeIndex。您可以使用 ``index_col`` "
"参数指定现有列作为索引。"

#: ../../source/user_guide/dataframe/io.rst:53
msgid ""
"If you want to store prepreocessed ``df`` into a MaxCompute table, you "
"can use :func:`to_odps_table` as is shown below."
msgstr ""
"如果您想要将预处理的 ``df`` 存储到大数据计算服务表中，您可以使用 :func:`"
"to_odps_table` 如下所示。"

#: ../../source/user_guide/dataframe/io.rst:60
msgid ""
"You can control the behavior of index output via ``index`` and "
"``index_label`` arguments. By default the index is outputted. If you do "
"not want to output the index, you may specify ``index`` argument as "
"False."
msgstr ""
"您可以通过 ``index`` 和 ``index_label`` 参数控制索引输出的行为。默认情况"
"下，索引会被输出。如果您不想输出索引，您可以将 ``index`` 参数设置为 False"
"。"

#: ../../source/user_guide/dataframe/io.rst:68
msgid ""
"The names of columns for indexes is the names of the indexes by default. "
"If names of indexes are not specified, the name ``index`` will be used if"
" the index only has one level, or ``level_x`` will be used, where ``x`` "
"is the integer index of the level."
msgstr ""
"默认情况下，索引列的名称是索引的名称。如果没有指定索引名，则如果索引只有"
"一个级别，将使用名称 ``index``，否则将使用 ``level_x``，其中 ``x`` 是级别"
"的整数索引。"

#: ../../source/user_guide/dataframe/io.rst:72
msgid ""
"Data can be stored as partitioned tables. You may specify ``partition`` "
"argument as the partition to write."
msgstr "数据可以存储为分区表。您可以将 ``partition`` 参数指定为要写的分区。"

#: ../../source/user_guide/dataframe/io.rst:79
msgid ""
"You can also specify columns as partition columns. The data of these "
"columns will dynamically decide the partition the row will be written to."
msgstr "您还可以指定列作为分区列。这些列的数据将动态决定行将被写入哪个分区。"

#: ../../source/user_guide/dataframe/io.rst:87
msgid "Read from SQL queries"
msgstr "从 SQL 查询读取"

#: ../../source/user_guide/dataframe/io.rst:88
msgid ""
"Users can create MaxFrame DataFrame objects with MaxCompute queries with "
":func:`read_odps_query`. MaxFrame will retrieve DataFrame schema with "
"`EXPLAIN <https://www.alibabacloud.com/help/zh/maxcompute/user-"
"guide/explain>`_ statement and execute queries in MaxCompute."
msgstr ""
"用户可以通过使用 :func:`read_odps_query` 来使用大数据计算服务查询创建 "
"MaxFrame DataFrame 对象。MaxFrame 将使用 `EXPLAIN <https://www."
"alibabacloud.com/help/zh/maxcompute/user-guide/explain>`_ 语句检索 "
"DataFrame 架构并在大数据计算服务中执行查询。"

#: ../../source/user_guide/dataframe/io.rst:93
msgid "For instance, you can create a DataFrame with SQL statement below."
msgstr "例如，您可以使用以下 SQL 语句创建一个 DataFrame。"

#: ../../source/user_guide/dataframe/io.rst:103
msgid "pandas objects"
msgstr "pandas 对象"

#: ../../source/user_guide/dataframe/io.rst:104
msgid ""
"Users can convert between local pandas objects and DataFrames with "
":func:`read_pandas` and :func:`DataFrame.to_pandas`."
msgstr ""
"用户可以通过使用 :func:`read_pandas` 和 :func:`DataFrame.to_pandas` 在"
"本地 pandas 对象和 DataFrame 之间进行转换。"

#: ../../source/user_guide/dataframe/io.rst:107
msgid ""
"When ``read_pandas`` is called, these pandas objects will be uploaded to "
"MaxCompute and be used in the cluster."
msgstr ""
"当调用 ``read_pandas`` 时，这些 pandas 对象将被上传到大数据计算服务并用于"
"集群。"

#: ../../source/user_guide/dataframe/io.rst:114
msgid ""
"After transformation is done in MaxFrame, data can be downloaded to "
"client with ``to_pandas``."
msgstr "在 MaxFrame 完成转换后，数据可以使用 ``to_pandas`` 下载到客户端。"

